text: Maisie Richardson-Sellers is a British actress. She is known for her recurring role as Eva Sinclair on The CW series The Originals. She also starred as King Saul of Israel's daughter Michal in the ABC Biblical series Of Kings and Prophets and as Amaya Jiwe / Vixen and Charlie on The CW superhero series Legends of Tomorrow. ==References== Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English voice actors Category:English stage actors Category:1991 births Category:Actors from London Category:Alumni of the University of Oxford Category:Black British actors
